727263f-a.title: Queens: Little Neck Parkway - 80th Avenue
727263f-a.text:
Little Neck Parkway, east side, opposite Eightieth Ave., showing,
E. Hultzz house in 1891, and the M. Wesnofski house and farm from
1896-1909. This house does not appear in the 1928 Atlas.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
